com.k2.Proxy

Class ClassProformaAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.k2.Proxy.ClassProformaAdapter

  • public class ClassProformaAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
    The class proforma adapter adapts an instance of the java Class object into an instance that provides values for the class proforma used to generate jave source code for the proxy for the given class.

    simon
